    OBJECT:   Defeat your prison pals in a friendly game of puzzle
              solving.  To the victor goes the spoils.  To the loser
              goes the amperage. 

    This program has been tested on an Amiga 500 with one meg of ram,
    an Amiga 1200, and an Amiga 2000.  Hard Drive recommended but not
    required.  1 Meg chip.


